overview: The Little Gym of Westboro is owned and operated by Anthony & Kellie Karpouzis who purchased the gym back in August of 2007. They are both perfectly suited to be owners of a The Little Gym, due primarily to Kellie’s 12+ years of gymnastics experience as well as working in pre-school for several years and Anthony’s 14 years as a lacrosse coach and an accounting/business background.
